column16: Darnell McDonald grounds into double play, shortstop J.   Hardy to second baseman Robert Andino to first baseman Mark Reynolds.    Dustin Pedroia out at 2nd.
Dustin Pedroia walks.    Ryan Sweeney to 2nd.
Ryan Sweeney singles on a line drive to second baseman Robert Andino, deflected by pitcher Chris Davis.
Mike Aviles doubles (8) on a line drive to center fielder Adam Jones.  Marlon Byrd out at home on the throw, center fielder Adam Jones to shortstop J.   Hardy to catcher Matt Wieters.
Marlon Byrd reaches on fielding error by third baseman Wilson Betemit.
Will Middlebrooks flies out to center fielder Adam Jones.
